Bot to repost one random image from your ootd channel into a new forum post based on month/year input. 

Channel where images are grabbed from must be configured to channel ID
Channel where forum post is announced must be configured to channel ID
Forum where thread is posted must be configured to channel ID

Usage:
!archive <month> <year>

Command will only work in a specifc private channel so you can limit to whoever you want able to run this
Has a limit to how many times a given month/year can be called (default 3)
Will only post to a specified forum channel
Can be configured to announce the new post in whatever channel (see above) 
Can handle the needle bot auto thread thing fine
Picks randomly from the month so not reaction based at all
No local storage, makes a new post, posts the images then deleted from memory
